name: Aura Quest Gen
tagline: Small java app to generate #.cs files containing Quest scripts for Aura
body:
### Aura Quest Generator.
Heavily under construction.
Simple java app to generate Quest scripts based on simple templates. Built for Project Aura.
You can check the original forum thread [here](http://aura-project.org/forum/topic/215-quest-generator/).

### Authors and Contributors
